{"tid":2057453,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"拾年舖面變文宣 x Fanling Hideout粉嶺私塾","createTime":"2020-06-09T11:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T08:22:01.000Z","uid":113263,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"64d748a3ba8551da3a6b395e76fa7068ecd43e0b","tid":2057453,"uid":113263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnFTLUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnFTLUZ.jpg&h=3b0bc39f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舖面變文宣嚟到第三間舖頭啦！今次喺位於粉嶺聯和墟嘅Fanling Hideout粉嶺私塾。<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺Hideout喺主打鬧市中慢活嘅生活態度，裝修好適合做野做到攰嘅時候去hea嘅好地方，文青可以過嚟睇吓書放鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MmfZcU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MmfZcU.jpg&h=24892dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWFHEcX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWFHEcX.jpg&h=378bb23b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URQTLSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURQTLSY.jpg&h=754959a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個讀書室嘅腦細，深深明白到知識嘅重要性，仲話「要打造一個美好嘅香港就必先裝備自己思想」，要嬴必先要裝備好自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅舖面變文宣特意搵嚟設計師「Dandan」（化名）。除咗讀緊書嘅pepe同連豬，<br />\n「Dandan」仲加入中華白海豚，希望大家可以多啲留意環境保育問題，至於隻狗就唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「歷史在此時就像是一張白紙，被不斷抹乾淨寫上新的內容。」<br />\n懇請各位共同守護我哋寶貴嘅香港文化。<br />\n#香港文化復興<br />\n<br />\n由於時間關係，添福嘅舖面變文宣會轉為幫設計者寄賣作品，善用及宣揚文宣設計者嘅作品，以支持佢哋喺文宣上嘅付出。<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n「一個人嘅無限付出可以變成每個人嘅舉手之勞」<br />\n拾年係由幾位大專生同中學生組成嘅公司，我哋會用市場推廣形式去協助壯大黃色經濟圈。我哋都會積極聯繫黃店舉辦唔同嘅社區活動比大家參與，係咁冷漠無情嘅商業社會下，我哋希望打破現有嘅商業模式，重拾充滿人情味嘅社會。<br />\n<br />\nFollow 拾年<br />\nApp store/Play store：拾年<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sapnin2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsapnin2019%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=7e6f3c0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sapnin2019/</a><br />\nInstagram：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/sap_nin?igshid=12o7m9k9o4st5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsap_nin%3Figshid%3D12o7m9k9o4st5&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=e35942e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/sap_nin?igshid=12o7m9k9o4st5</a> <br />\n拾年Telegram：<a href=\"https://t.me/sapnin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsapnin&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=f012637a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sapnin</a> <br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\nFanling Hideout<br />\nIG ＠fanlinghideou<br />\nFB @fanlinghideou<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n已完成舖面變文宣活動之店舖<br />\n-鮨葵：上水新祥街2-28號<br />\n-三姐妹：鴨脷洲利東邨道5號利東街市48-50號舖<br />\n-Fanling Hideout：粉嶺粉嶺樓1K號"},{"pid":"db3e228d53a2d392fbdba978dbe9657d96f37c05","tid":2057453,"uid":113263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cc825841bae5ce3a6ba6572b35b6760a30fd19","tid":2057453,"uid":113263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64f30900e4f6e35126e15276f5b2375e01d29d6","tid":2057453,"uid":113263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3e5b9f953642f266880465796e3fdfbd34bb2b